"Here’s what you need to know","tagName":"h3","type":"CORE_HEADING"},"YmxvY2s6WTI5c2JHVmpkR2x2YmpveE9URTNNVEV5fDI=":{"__typename":"Block","connections":[],"attributes":[{"__typename":"Attribute","name":"dateModified","value":"1602683016"}],"id":"YmxvY2s6WTI5c2JHVmpkR2x2YmpveE9URTNNVEV5fDI=","innerHtml":"\u003Cstrong\u003EWall Street weighs in.\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E Bank of America📉, Wells Fargo📉, Goldman Sachs📈,  US Bancorp📈, and PNC 📈 reported quarterly earnings on Wednesday.  While major banks are putting away less cash to cover for bad loans, megabank CEOs are urging \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.wsj.com\u002Farticles\u002Fjpmorgan-citigroup-signal-that-economy-isnt-out-of-the-woods-11602611732?mod=hp_lead_pos1\"\u003Emore US fiscal stimulus\u003C\u002Fa\u003E to boost economic recovery.","tagName":"p","type":"CORE_PARAGRAPH"},"YmxvY2s6WTI5c2JHVmpkR2x2YmpveE9URTNNVEV5fDQ=":{"__typename":"Block","connections":[],"attributes":[{"__typename":"Attribute","name":"dateModified","value":"1602683637"}],"id":"YmxvY2s6WTI5c2JHVmpkR2x2YmpveE9URTNNVEV5fDQ=","innerHtml":"\u003Cstrong\u003EChina’s stock market value topped $10 trillion.\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E The \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.ft.com\u002Fcontent\u002F7e2d1cae-8033-45b1-811c-bc7d4a413e33\"\u003Efive-year-high\u003C\u002Fa\u003E coincided with a \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.scmp.com\u002Fnews\u002Fchina\u002Fpolitics\u002Farticle\u002F3105483\u002Fxi-jinping-shenzhen-model-innovation-and-reform-drive-chinas\"\u003Esignificant economic speech\u003C\u002Fa\u003E from Xi Jinping marking the 40th anniversary of the Shenzhen special economic zone that called for an expansion of the SEZ model.","tagName":"p","type":"CORE_PARAGRAPH"},"YmxvY2s6WTI5c2JHVmpkR2x2YmpveE9URTNNVEV5fDY=":{"__typename":"Block","connections":[],"attributes":[],"id":"YmxvY2s6WTI5c2JHVmpkR2x2YmpveE9URTNNVEV5fDY=","innerHtml":"\u003Cstrong\u003EApple is changing the way we charge phones.\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E The 5G-enabled iPhone 12 \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.theverge.com\u002F2020\u002F10\u002F13\u002F21508028\u002Fapple-iphone-12-pro-max-homepod-mini-event-recap-biggest-announcements\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003Ecomes in three sizes\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, but will \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fqz.com\u002F1917088\u002Fapples-iphone-12-could-revolutionize-the-future-of-charging\u002F?utm_source=email&utm_medium=daily-brief&utm_content=9956871\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003Eno longer include a charger\u003C\u002Fa\u003E or wired headphones. At the same time, Verizon announced the rollout of its US 5G network.","tagName":"p","type":"CORE_PARAGRAPH"},"YmxvY2s6WTI5c2JHVmpkR2x2YmpveE9URTNNVEV5fDg=":{"__typename":"Block","connections":[],"attributes":[],"id":"YmxvY2s6WTI5c2JHVmpkR2x2YmpveE9URTNNVEV5fDg=","innerHtml":"\u003Cstrong\u003EStevie Wonder left Motown.\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.billboard.com\u002Famp\u002Farticles\u002Fnews\u002F9464244\u002Fstevie-wonder-leaves-motown-releasing-new-songs-what-fuss\"\u003EThe legendary musician launched his own imprint\u003C\u002Fa\u003E with Republic Records, nearly 60 years after signing for Berry Gordy’s equally legendary label at the age of just 11. He also announced two new songs.","tagName":"p","type":"CORE_PARAGRAPH"},"YmxvY2s6WTI5c2JHVmpkR2x2YmpveE9URTNNVEV5fDEw":{"__typename":"Block","connections":[],"attributes":[],"id":"YmxvY2s6WTI5c2JHVmpkR2x2YmpveE9URTNNVEV5fDEw","innerHtml":"","tagName":"hr","type":"CORE_SEPARATOR"},"YmxvY2s6Ym5Wbk9qRTVNVGN4TnpBPXww":{"__typename":"Block","connections":[],"attributes":[],"id":"YmxvY2s6Ym5Wbk9qRTVNVGN4TnpBPXww","innerHtml":"Disney had no streaming platforms three years ago. Today, its business revolves around them. On Monday, the company announced a “strategic reorganization” to further prop up its streaming services: Disney+, ESPN+, and Hulu. Effective immediately, Disney will separate content creation from distribution.","tagName":"p","type":"CORE_PARAGRAPH"},"YmxvY2s6Ym5Wbk9qRTVNVGN4TnpBPXwy":{"__typename":"Block","connections":[],"attributes":[{"__typename":"Attribute","name":"url","value":"https:\u002F\u002Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net\u002F3HRoz\u002F1\u002F"},{"__typename":"Attribute","name":"type","value":"rich"},{"__typename":"Attribute","name":"providerNameSlug","value":"datawrapper"},{"__typename":"Attribute","name":"className","value":""},{"__typename":"Attribute","name":"dateModified","value":"1602626327"},{"__typename":"Attribute","name":"width","value":"600"},{"__typename":"Attribute","name":"height","value":"400"}],"id":"YmxvY2s6Ym5Wbk9qRTVNVGN4TnpBPXwy","innerHtml":"\nhttps:\u002F\u002Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net\u002F3HRoz\u002F1\u002F\n","tagName":"figure","type":"EMBED_DATAWRAPPER"},"YmxvY2s6Ym5Wbk9qRTVNVGN4TnpBPXw0":{"__typename":"Block","connections":[],"attributes":[],"id":"YmxvY2s6Ym5Wbk9qRTVNVGN4TnpBPXw0","innerHtml":"The Mouse House will not abandon cinemas, but its reorganization is an admission that theaters do not represent the future of the company—or perhaps of any Hollywood content company. \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fqz.com\u002F1916923\u002Frecent-changes-at-disney-prioritize-hulu-disney-and-espn\u002F\"\u003EAdam Epstein tunes us in on Disney’s fast-forward to streaming\u003C\u002Fa\u003E.","tagName":"p","type":"CORE_PARAGRAPH"},"bnVnOjE5MTcxNzA=":{"__typename":"Nug","id":"bnVnOjE5MTcxNzA=","blocks":[{"__ref":"YmxvY2s6Ym5Wbk9qRTVNVGN4TnpBPXww"},{"__ref":"YmxvY2s6Ym5Wbk9qRTVNVGN4TnpBPXwy"},{"__ref":"YmxvY2s6Ym5Wbk9qRTVNVGN4TnpBPXw0"}],"dateGmt":"2020-10-13T21:58:51","emailLists":{"__typename":"NugToEmailListConnection","edges":[]},"link":"https:\u002F\u002Fqz.com\u002Fbriefing\u002F1917170\u002Fcharting-disneys-streaming-metamorphosis\u002F","modifiedGmt":"2020-10-13T21:58:51","nugId":1917170,"tags":{"__typename":"NugToTagConnection","nodes":[]},"topics":{"__typename":"NugToTopicConnection","nodes":[]},"slug":"charting-disneys-streaming-metamorphosis","title":"Charting Disney’s s